<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Login Security Alert</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #dc3545; /* Red color for security alert */
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Security Alert: Login Notification</h1>
    <p>Dear {{email}},</p>
    <p>A login to your account was detected.</p>
    <p><strong>Details:</strong></p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Login Time:</strong> {{loginTime}}</li>
    </ul>
    <p>If this was not you, please take immediate action to secure your account.</p>
    <p>Best regards,</p>
    <footer>Your App Team</footer>
</body>
</html>
